&lt;h2>Linting&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="linting">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#linting" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>To run golangci-lint:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">golangci-lint run&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0">
&lt;button
class="hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50"
title="Copy code"
>
&lt;div class="hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;/button>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>It&amp;rsquo;s an equivalent of:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">golangci-lint run ./...&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0">
&lt;button
class="hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50"
title="Copy code"
>
&lt;div class="hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;/button>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>You can choose which directories or files to analyze:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">golangci-lint run dir1 dir2/...
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">golangci-lint run file1.go&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0">
&lt;button
class="hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50"
title="Copy code"
>
&lt;div class="hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;/button>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>Directories are NOT analyzed recursively.
To analyze them recursively append &lt;code>/...&lt;/code> to their path.
It&amp;rsquo;s not possible to mix files and packages/directories, and files must come from the same package.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Golangci-lint can be used with zero configuration. By default, the following linters are enabled:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-console" data-lang="console">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="gp">$&lt;/span> golangci-lint &lt;span class="nb">help&lt;/span> linters
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="go">Enabled by default linters:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="go">errcheck: Errcheck is a program for checking for unchecked errors in Go code. These unchecked errors can be critical bugs in some cases.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="go">govet: Vet examines Go source code and reports suspicious constructs. It is roughly the same as &amp;#39;go vet&amp;#39; and uses its passes. [auto-fix]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="go">ineffassign: Detects when assignments to existing variables are not used. [fast]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="go">staticcheck: It&amp;#39;s the set of rules from staticcheck. [auto-fix]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="go">unused: Checks Go code for unused constants, variables, functions and types.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0">
&lt;button
class="hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50"
title="Copy code"
>
&lt;div class="hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;/button>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>Pass &lt;code>-E/--enable&lt;/code> to enable linter and &lt;code>-D/--disable&lt;/code> to disable:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">golangci-lint run --default&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>none -E errcheck&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0">
&lt;button
class="hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50"
title="Copy code"
>
&lt;div class="hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;/button>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>More information about available linters can be found in the &lt;a href="https://golangci-lint.run/docs/linters/">linters page&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2>Formatting&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="formatting">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#formatting" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>To format your code:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">golangci-lint fmt&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0">
&lt;button
class="hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50"
title="Copy code"
>
&lt;div class="hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;/button>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>You can choose which directories or files to analyze:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">golangci-lint fmt dir1 dir2/...
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">golangci-lint fmt file1.go&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0">
&lt;button
class="hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50"
title="Copy code"
>
&lt;div class="hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;/button>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>More information about available formatters can be found in the &lt;a href="https://golangci-lint.run/docs/formatters/">formatters page&lt;/a>.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Integrations</title><link>https://golangci-lint.run/docs/welcome/integrations/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://golangci-lint.run/docs/welcome/integrations/</guid><description>
&lt;h2>Editor Integration&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="editor-integration">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#editor-integration" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;h3>GoLand&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="goland">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#goland" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Starting from version 2025.1, GoLand has built-in support of golangci-lint.
For IntelliJ IDEA with the Go plugin, please install the &lt;a href="https://plugins.jetbrains.com/plugin/12496-go-linter"target="_blank" rel="noopener">plugin&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Both v1 and v2 versions are supported.&lt;/p>
&lt;h3>Visual Studio Code&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="visual-studio-code">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#visual-studio-code" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Install the &lt;a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=golang.Go"target="_blank" rel="noopener">extension&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;details class="hx:last-of-type:mb-0 hx:rounded-lg hx:bg-neutral-50 hx:dark:bg-neutral-800 hx:p-2 hx:mt-4 hx:group" >
&lt;summary class="hx:flex hx:items-center hx:cursor-pointer hx:select-none hx:list-none hx:p-1 hx:rounded-sm hx:transition-colors hx:hover:bg-gray-100 hx:dark:hover:bg-neutral-800 hx:before:mr-1 hx:before:inline-block hx:before:transition-transform hx:before:content-[''] hx:dark:before:invert hx:rtl:before:rotate-180 hx:group-open:before:rotate-90">
&lt;span class="hx:text-lg">Recommended settings for those who installed golangci-lint manually&lt;/span>
&lt;/summary>
&lt;div class="hx:p-2 hx:overflow-hidden">
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-JSONata" data-lang="JSONata">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;go.lintTool&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;golangci-lint&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;go.lintFlags&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;--path-mode=abs&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;--fast-only&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">],&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;go.formatTool&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;custom&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;go.alternateTools&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;customFormatter&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;golangci-lint&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">},&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;go.formatFlags&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;fmt&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;--stdin&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">]&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0">
&lt;button
class="hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50"
title="Copy code"
>
&lt;div class="hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;/button>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>Using it in an editor without &lt;code>--fast-only&lt;/code> can freeze your editor.
Golangci-lint automatically discovers the &lt;code>.golangci.yml&lt;/code> config for the edited file, so you don&amp;rsquo;t need to configure it in VS Code settings.&lt;/p>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/details>
&lt;details class="hx:last-of-type:mb-0 hx:rounded-lg hx:bg-neutral-50 hx:dark:bg-neutral-800 hx:p-2 hx:mt-4 hx:group" >
&lt;summary class="hx:flex hx:items-center hx:cursor-pointer hx:select-none hx:list-none hx:p-1 hx:rounded-sm hx:transition-colors hx:hover:bg-gray-100 hx:dark:hover:bg-neutral-800 hx:before:mr-1 hx:before:inline-block hx:before:transition-transform hx:before:content-[''] hx:dark:before:invert hx:rtl:before:rotate-180 hx:group-open:before:rotate-90">
&lt;span class="hx:text-lg">Recommended settings for those who installed golangci-lint via extension&lt;/span>
&lt;/summary>
&lt;div class="hx:p-2 hx:overflow-hidden">
&lt;p>Install &lt;code>golangci-lint-v2&lt;/code> via the &lt;code>Go: Install/Update Tools&lt;/code> command after setting these configs.
This will enable golangci-lint v1 to co-exist with v2.
And use the following settings:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-JSONata" data-lang="JSONata">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;go.lintTool&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;golangci-lint-v2&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;go.lintFlags&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;--path-mode=abs&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;--fast-only&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">],&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;go.formatTool&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;custom&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;go.alternateTools&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;customFormatter&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;golangci-lint-v2&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">},&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;go.formatFlags&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;fmt&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;--stdin&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">]&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0">
&lt;button
class="hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50"
title="Copy code"
>
&lt;div class="hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;/button>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>Using it in an editor without &lt;code>--fast-only&lt;/code> can freeze your editor.
Golangci-lint automatically discovers the &lt;code>.golangci.yml&lt;/code> config for the edited file, so you don&amp;rsquo;t need to configure it in VS Code settings.&lt;/p>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/details>
&lt;h3>GNU Emacs&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="gnu-emacs">&lt;/span>
