&lt;a href="#lsp-server" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://github.com/nametake/golangci-lint-langserver"target="_blank" rel="noopener">golangci-lint-langserver&lt;/a> (NeoVim, Vim, Emacs, &amp;hellip;)&lt;/p>
